#                 ⎛  ⎛     -α⋅lv ⎞⎞
#                 ⎜π⋅⎝1 - 2    ⋅C⎠⎟
#  Threshold = tan⎜───────────────⎟
#                 ⎝       2       ⎠
#
#   where (1) C is the constant determined by the threshold at root level
#         (2) α is the constant which adjust the convergence speed to 90 degree
#
